data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This exquisite 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence seamlessly combines contemporary elegance with functional design, creating a haven that caters to both comfort and style - upon entering, you'll be greeted by a tastefully designed living room bathed in natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere - the gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring stainless appliances, granite countertops, and ample cabinet space for all your culinary adventures - the primary suite is a true retreat, boasting a generous layout, a connected flex or office space, and a luxurious en-suite bathroom with a spa-like ambiance - upstairs features the spacious 4th bedroom or it can be used as a game or media room to suit your specific needs - the meticulously landscaped backyard is an extension of the living space, offering a private oasis for relaxation and outdoor gatherings - don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home and schedule your tour today!
